Welcome to IRM!

All of the documentation for IRM is location in the docs directory of this
installation.  Please browse there for more information.  Of particular
interest:

INSTALL -- complete installation instructions for the first-time IRM user.

UPGRADE -- important points to note when performing an upgrade from a
	previous version of IRM to this one.

RELEASE_NOTES -- Useful bits of information about this release of IRM, such
	as important new features or critical bugfixes.  You should read
	this with each new release of IRM.

There are also several other files of interest to users and developers in
the docs directory.
